column5: Couldn't resist taking a picture of this likely looking shelter, seems about the right size.
Know anyone with a boom truck... 4 tabs on top... it's ready to go
Here's one for ya that already has the hole in the bottom!
I believe she's got two holes in the bottom!! LOL

Now Paul when are you going to find an ice shelter that suits you.  All I can say is your one tough old bugger when it gets cold ice fishin wide open with just a wind shelter and no heater.  No thanks give me my Frabill ice shelter and my 3000 BTU coleman propane heater.That is the way i like it.  MTP
